IMPORTANT NOTICE FOR ILLINOIS CONSUMERS
AXIS Insurance Companies have implemented all requirements outlined in Illinois Department of Insurance Bulletin 2015-13 (Revised) pertaining to Illinois consumers affected by the current flooding disaster. Complaints regarding any disaster-related dispute or issue may be filed with the Illinois Department of Insurance by calling toll-free complaint hotline 1-866-445-5364 or by filing a complaint online at 
   https://mc.insurance.illinois.gov/messagecenter.nsf











