Our Culture and Values
AXIS is a global insurer and reinsurer, providing our clients and distribution partners a broad range of risk transfer products and services, meaningful capacity and unquestioned financial strength.
We nurture an ethical, entrepreneurial and disciplined culture that promotes outstanding client service, intelligent risk taking and superior risk-adjusted returns for our shareholders.
At AXIS we nurture an ethical, risk-aware, achievement-oriented culture that promotes professionalism, responsibility, integrity, discipline, and entrepreneurialism.













Home
    

    > Reinsurance


                AXIS Re
                
            





AXIS Re is a leading diversified global reinsurer. We provide risk transfer products, primarily in the form of reinsurance contracts, offering meaningful capacity and unquestioned financial strength.  Our innovative specialty solutions for clients include treaty and facultative property and casualty reinsurance to insurance companies on a worldwide basis comprising catastrophe, property, professional lines, credit and surety, motor, general liability, engineering, marine, workers' compensation and agriculture.



Widget Image
 

The AXIS Re AdvantageOur highly disciplined and experienced underwriting, claims, modeling and actuarial teams at AXIS Re have a breadth and depth of knowledge that distinguishes us in the industry. Clients around the globe value our expert underwriting, skilled claims management, outstanding service and world-class product offerings all backed by exceptional financial strength.Our goal of maintaining sustainable and profitable relationships with clients is built on a foundation of specialty knowledge, quality data and analytics, transparency in pricing and candid, open dialogue. We nurture an ethical, entrepreneurial and disciplined culture that promotes intelligent risk taking and the empowerment of our reinsurance professionals.Global Centers of ExcellenceIn the global economy, the quality of your reinsurance support is only as strong as the underwriting expertise to which you have access.  AXIS Re brings that quality to our clients around the world with global centers of excellence strategically situated to reflect the principal locations where insurance companies purchase reinsurance.  All of our locations, including Bermuda, New York, Singapore, Toronto and Zurich provide clients with highly rated capital and the industry's most experienced underwriting teams.


